{"tid":2420960,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓星確診第一人　金請夏癒後憂鬱自責：好像全都我的錯！","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T08:08:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9fffdb3cdb8c3b2253356bac6ca92cb5a288b654","tid":2420960,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"前女團組合I.O.I高人氣成員，南韓25歲SOLO女歌手金請夏（김청하），因12月7日確診武漢肺炎（COVID-19，新冠肺炎）在娛樂圈引發軒然大波，成為本土病例藝人的第一人，所幸透過治療後目前已痊癒，更帶著最新作品《Bicycle》回歸，她談到當初確診的心情，憂鬱自責地透露：「確診新冠肺炎好像全是我的錯。」甚至牽連周遭朋友們，令她感到很難過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/16/3027944-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F3027944-PH.jpg&h=f8c1c85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請夏痊癒後，接受節目《On&amp;Off》訪問透露「我是藝人中第一個確診」聊起治療過程和痊癒的心情，她表示：「好像全是我的錯，因為我是大眾人物，所以我不斷祈禱，祈禱我是藝人中確診的最後一個，因為真的牽涉到太多了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/16/3027936-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F3027936-PH.jpg&h=d4359812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金請夏個人首張專輯《Querencia》延宕數月正式推出。（圖／翻攝自金請夏IG）<br />\n<br />\n回想去年證實確診後經歷：「幸好我知道了自己是確診者而沒有到處走動，也因為有遵守隔離守則而痊癒了，我是無症狀患者，現在已完全康復，因為是無症狀患者，所以沒有覺得辛苦，也沒發燒，但正是因為這樣我更覺得害怕，不過我一個人想了很多，不過也覺得很感恩。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/16/3027942-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2F3027942-PH.jpg&h=1074021f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲請夏坦言知道自己染疫時感到很害怕。（圖／翻攝自金請夏IG）<br />\n<br />\n她這張首張專輯《Querencia》推出前「毫無症狀」，正要開始進行宣傳期全部停擺，並接受相關指示進行隔離治療，再錄影片回報給醫生與護理師，最終獲得痊癒判定，只見她嫵媚性感跳唱，狀態看似相當不錯，該專輯音樂幕後團隊則是由張榕容的老公歌手紀佳松幕後操刀製作。"},{"pid":"9adb94fca38d3b40d9037d6644e5ec45c931d915","tid":2420960,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲客套說話嚟嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9befcc34c86a596cb6667bd8c50498f4e09a1ae2","tid":2420960,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9adb94fca38d3b40d9037d6644e5ec45c931d915","tid":2420960,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲客套說話嚟嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"正蠢才<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f0b20339534154bc1219213d1da62fbff6677a","tid":2420960,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9adb94fca38d3b40d9037d6644e5ec45c931d915","tid":2420960,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲客套說話嚟嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:04:48.000Z","msg":"我愛你..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b88031bd135d16360337f3d85651f4efc0898c","tid":2420960,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9befcc34c86a596cb6667bd8c50498f4e09a1ae2","tid":2420960,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9adb94fca38d3b40d9037d6644e5ec45c931d915","tid":2420960,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲客套說話嚟嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"正蠢才<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"Feel 唔到佢有嘅愧疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i